        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "忽听窑外有人捶，\n想必平郎转回归。\n为何这身荣耀回？"
        },
        {
          "character": "用手开门来观看、王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，平郎回来了，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平郎，哪里来的这身荣耀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姐哪里知道，只因红纱洞中，出了妖魔伤人。唐王出了榜文在外，有人降了\n妖魔，高官任做，骏马任骑。是为夫的揭了榜文，前去降妖，谁知乃是一匹红\n鬃烈马，是我将它降住，唐王见喜，封我后军都督府。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恭喜平郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢，这喜中有变！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎样有变？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可恨你父，上殿参奏一本，将我后营都督府，改为马前先行。谁知西凉下国造\n反，圣上命苏龙、魏虎挂帅，命我做他先行，此番前去，不知三年五载，因此\n回得寒窑，与三姐一别。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你待怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与你一别。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏气椅。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姐醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听他言唬得我心惊胆怕，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平郎！我夫！吓夫吓吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恨爹爹害平郎启奏皇家。\n父好比汉萧何私造律法；\n父好比毛延寿怀抱琵琶。\n害平郎赶女儿所为哪般？"
        },
        {
          "character": "父好比秦赵高指鹿为马、父好比奸曹操进宫迫驾、身为了宰相家全不怕被人来骂、薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姐吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "父好比秦赵高指鹿为马、父好比奸曹操进宫迫驾、身为了宰相家全不怕被人来骂、薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "说什么秦赵高指鹿为马，\n说什么汉萧何私造律法；\n说什么毛延寿怀抱琵琶。\n苦害我薛平贵所为哪般？"
        },
        {
          "character": "说什么奸曹操进宫迫驾、你的父与平贵把仇结下、王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "对着相府高声骂，\n害得我夫平郎难以归家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "耳边听得号炮炸，\n想必是魏虎贼把兵发。"
        },
        {
          "character": "辞别三姐把马跨、王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "扯住衣衿不松开。\n平郎夫吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "你要走来将奴带、薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "苦苦拉我为何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "此去定有三五载，\n你把为妻怎安排？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姐吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "三姐不必泪双流，\n平贵言来听从头：\n你在寒窑度春秋。\n守不得我来把我丢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "十担干柴米八斗、守得我来你就守、王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "十担干柴米八斗、守得我来你就守、王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "平郎说话莫来由，\n妻子言来听从头：\n女嫁二夫骂名流。\n富贵荣华一旦丢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马备双鞍路难走、三年五载将你守、守得不过你也要守、饿死寒窑不回头、薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "好个三姐世少有，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平贵听令：元帅身坐教场，连点二卯，再有一卯不到，按军令示刑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军不下马，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "各自奔前程。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "适才何人到来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "中军到此，言道元帅身坐教场，连点二卯，再有一卯不到，要按军令示刑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "几时起程？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "即刻起程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为妻送你一程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳三姐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "手挽平郎出窑门，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "平贵带过马缰绳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你往西凉身保稳，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你在寒窑守孤灯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "但愿旗开早得胜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自有书信到窑门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "送夫送到西河岸，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呕呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫人难舍又难分。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "空中降下无情剑，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "斩断夫妻两离分。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "流泪眼观流泪眼，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "断肠人送断肠人，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "王宝钏舍不得薛平贵，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "薛平贵难舍妻宝钏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呕呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "夫妻们分别难得见，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫吓，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "实实难舍夫妻情。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内鼓声。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "耳边厢听得鸣锣鼓，\n莫不是魏虎把兵发。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姐，为丈夫去了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵推。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "得胜回来转回家。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平郎，吾夫，吓夫吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见平郎上能行，\n不由妻子挂在心。\n只等得胜报喜音。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓夫吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏哭下。）"
        }
      ],
